                    And so the Handsome Farmer and the Dark-Haired Nurse at last met and their love story began. As the days and the weeks went by, their hearts became entwined in eternal love and the Handsome Farmer asked the father of the Dark-Haired Nurse for her hand. The father of course said, “Yes, take her away to the farm!” And so they were married and away they went to the farm and they promised forever to be true to each other for ever and ever (the words of both the Handsome Farmer and the Dark-Haired Nurse)!
